OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782485286
OL,3,CGerman Christmas market attacker
OL,4,Csentenced to life
OL,6,FA Saudi doctor who killed six people
OL,7,Fin a car-ramming attack on a Christmas
OL,8,Fmarket in the German city of Magdeburg
OL,9,Fin 2024 has been sentenced to life in
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FA court found that Taleb al-
OL,13,FAbdulmohsen, 51, carries "particularly
OL,14,Fserious" guilt, German news agency dpa
OL,15,Freported. That means he won't be
OL,16,Feligible for release after 15 years as
OL,17,Fis usually the case in Germany.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
