OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782485286
OL,3,CGerman Christmas market attacker
OL,4,Csentenced to life
OL,6,FFive women and a boy died, and many
OL,7,Fmore people were wounded, in the
OL,8,Fattack on December 20, 2024, which
OL,9,Flasted just over a minute.
OL,11,FThe attack was carried out with a
OL,12,Frented BMW X3, which reached speeds of
OL,13,Fup to 48 kph (30 mph) during the
OL,14,Frampage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
