PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782485286
OL,3,CGerman Christmas market attacker
OL,4,Csentenced to life
OL,6,FInvestigators said when they filed the
OL,7,Findictment that the defendant wasn't
OL,8,Funder the influence of alcohol, and
OL,9,Fapparently acted out of
OL,10,Fdissatisfaction with the outcome of a
OL,11,Flegal dispute and the failure of
OL,12,Fvarious criminal complaints.
OL,14,FThey also have said that he planned
OL,15,Fthe attack without accomplices.
OL,16,FOfficials have said the suspect
OL,17,Fdoesn't fit the usual profile of
OL,18,Fperpetrators of extremist attacks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
