OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe defendant described himself as an
OL,12,Fex-Muslim who was highly critical of
OL,13,FIslam, and on social media expressed
OL,14,Fsupport for the far-right.
OL,16,FHe had previously come to authorities'
OL,17,Fattention for threatening behaviour
OL,18,Fbut wasn't known to have committed any
OL,19,Fviolence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
