OL,3,CGerman Christmas market attacker
OL,4,Csentenced to life
OL,6,FThe Magdeburg car-ramming was one of a
OL,7,Fseries of attacks involving immigrants
OL,8,Fthat pushed migration to the forefront
OL,9,Fof the campaign for Germany's national
OL,10,Felection in February 2025.
OL,12,FAl-Abdulmohsen arrived in Germany in
OL,13,F2006 and had received permanent
OL,14,Fresidency.
